02:02.539 --> 02:06.292
Look at him, Grandpa!
Ask him!

02:06.376 --> 02:09.002
Ryan, that's enough.

02:10.255 --> 02:12.590
Um, I'm sorry.

02:12.674 --> 02:15.259
He, uh—
He thinks you're Santa Claus.

02:23.018 --> 02:25.853
I am.

02:27.481 --> 02:31.317
- Merry Christmas.
- Uh, merry Christmas.

02:32.569 --> 02:35.029
Nuts. I should have
got his autograph.

