02:49.419 --> 02:52.171
♪ O'er the fields we go ♪

02:52.256 --> 02:55.132
♪ Laughing all the way ♪

02:55.217 --> 02:58.010
♪ Bells on bobtail ring ♪

02:58.095 --> 03:00.555
♪ Making spirits bright ♪

03:00.639 --> 03:03.558
♪ Oh, what fun it is to laugh and sing ♪

03:03.642 --> 03:05.810
♪ A sleighing song tonight ♪

03:05.894 --> 03:09.689
♪ Oh, jingle bells ♪
